This program requires cucumber, respec, and webrat to run the tests, along wth the rails gems.

To begin, start the development server:
$ ruby script/server  

Then, to create and populate the database with sample data:
$ rake db:migrate && rake db:seed

From there you may load the program in your web browser by going to:
http://localhost:3000

To run the tests, from the rails root directory:
$ cucumber


Documentation for the application can be found in
RAILS_ROOT/doc/app
